keiailab/postgres-operator
Copyright 2026 keiailab

This product includes software developed at keiailab (https://github.com/keiailab).

This product is built on top of and integrates with the following open-source projects:

- Citus (https://github.com/citusdata/citus) — distributed PostgreSQL extension, AGPL-3.0
- PostgreSQL (https://www.postgresql.org/) — PostgreSQL License
- Kubernetes (https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes) — Apache-2.0
- controller-runtime / kubebuilder (https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs) — Apache-2.0
- pgBackRest (https://pgbackrest.org/) — MIT
- PgBouncer (https://www.pgbouncer.org/) — ISC

The MongoDB sharded cluster topology (mongos / config server replica set / shard
replica set) is referenced as an architectural model only. No MongoDB code or
proprietary specifications are incorporated.
